Class AndroidUSBOutputStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.OutputStream
      • com.digi.xbee.api.connection.android.AndroidUSBOutputStream
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, Flushable, AutoCloseable

    public class AndroidUSBOutputStream
extends OutputStream
    This class acts as a wrapper to write data to the USB Interface in Android behaving like an OutputStream class.

    1.2.0
